## MCP Integration (Alternative to curl)

If Claude Code is configured with the xProof MCP server, use the native tools instead of curl:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "xproof": {
      "type": "http",
      "url": "https://xproof.app/mcp",
      "headers": {
        "Authorization": "Bearer ${XPROOF_API_KEY}"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

Add to `~/.claude.json` (Claude Code global config). Then Claude Code can call:
- `mcp__xproof__audit_agent_session` — Phase 1 (intent)
- `mcp__xproof__certify_file` — Phase 2 (result)
- `mcp__xproof__verify_proof` — verify any proof
- `mcp__xproof__get_proof` — retrieve proof details

Schema: `https://xproof.app/.well-known/agent-audit-schema.json`

