## /ship Integration

Add `/proof` naturally into the ostack workflow:

```
/plan-eng-review        # architect review
/proof --before "ship"  # anchor the intent → proof_before
[/ship executes]        # push, PR, tests
/proof --after          # anchor the diff → proof_after
                        # paste both URLs in the PR body
```

The PR description becomes a tamper-proof receipt: anyone can verify what Claude Code decided to ship — and what it actually changed — directly on the MultiversX blockchain.

